member.remarks:
The static friction compensation is given by:

if (abs(commandedSpeed) < minTriggerSpeed) {
	scale = 0
} else if (abs(commandedSpeed) > maxTriggerSpeed) {
	scale = 1;
} else {
	scale=(abs(commandedSpeed)-minTriggerSpeed) / (maxTriggerSpeed-minTriggerSpeed);
}
maxValue = (commandedSpeed > 0) ? maximumPositiveValue : maximumNegativeValue;
torque = maxValue * scale;
